OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer's visit to Northern
OL,7,FIreland has "raised expectations" that
OL,8,Fhe will act on the high cost of fuel,
OL,9,Fthe Sinn Fein leader has said.
OL,11,FMary Lou McDonald said the cost of
OL,12,Fliving was the main topic discussed
OL,13,Fduring a "very forthright" meeting
OL,14,Fwith Sir Keir in Belfast on Thursday.
OL,16,FShe and First Minister for Northern
OL,17,FIreland Michelle O'Neill said that
OL,18,Ffamilies were struggling with high
OL,19,Fcosts, as around two-thirds of
OL,20,Fdomestic properties in Northern
OL,21,FIreland use home heating oil.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@aO]uD@JOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
