OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FHe was meeting with the political
OL,7,Fleaders at Stormont before attending
OL,8,Fthe UK-Ireland Summit in Cork, along
OL,9,Fwith several senior ministers from his
OL,10,FCabinet.
OL,12,FSir Keir was meeting with the
OL,13,Fpolitical leaders at Stormont before
OL,14,Fattending the UK-Ireland Summit in
OL,15,FCork, along with several senior
OL,16,Fministers from his Cabinet.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
