PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FThe meeting comes as Sir Keir faces
OL,7,Frenewed questioning over making Lord
OL,8,FPeter Mandelson the UK's Washington
OL,9,Fambassador after a release of official
OL,10,Fdocuments revealed he had been warned
OL,11,Fof a "general reputational risk" over
OL,12,Fthe appointment.
OL,14,FIt also comes as governments are
OL,15,Fcoming under pressure over a spike in
OL,16,Fthe cost of fuel and home heating oil
OL,17,Fafter the US and Israel began bombing
OL,18,FIran over a week ago.
OL,26,@sD@FOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FMs McDonald said in Belfast: "We've
OL,7,Fchallenged the Prime Minister now to
OL,8,Fmake an announcement, to come up with
OL,9,Fsomething that will actually make a
OL,10,Fdifference to households right across
OL,11,Fthe north that are struggling so badly
OL,12,Fand who, thus far, have not seen any
OL,13,Fkind of an adequate response from
OL,14,FLondon, from the Prime Minister or
OL,15,Ffrom the Treasury."
OL,17,FShe added: "Keir Starmer has come to
OL,18,FIreland, to Belfast, to Cork.
OL,26,@nD@^OUwD@SO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,F"He has framed his visit in respect of
OL,7,Fcost-of-living pressures, and
OL,8,Fspecifically the price gouging, but
OL,9,Falso the runaway cost of home heating
OL,10,Foil, and he needs to come up with an
OL,11,Fanswer for families all across the
OL,12,Fnorth.
OL,14,F"I fully expect, and we've made this
OL,15,Fplain to him, that he will have
OL,16,Fsomething constructive and meaningful
OL,17,Fto say in that regard when he comes
OL,18,Fand speaks to the press."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
