OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said it
OL,7,Fstrikes "a strange chord" that
OL,8,Fpolitical leaders in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fwould call on Sir Keir to act on high
OL,10,Fenergy prices when there was funding
OL,11,F"waiting to be dispensed".
OL,13,FHe said actions that could be taken on
OL,14,Fsoaring fuel costs and "levers at his
OL,15,Fdisposal" were a particular topic on
OL,16,FSir Keir's agenda on Thursday.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@YO]sD@AOUsD@YO]vD@XOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FMr Robinson said: "He was as aghast as
OL,7,FI was to discover that #81 million is
OL,8,Fsitting there waiting to be dispensed,
OL,9,Fto assist consumers in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, and yet we have an economy
OL,11,Fminister that hasn't started work on a
OL,12,Fbusiness case, and a party that still
OL,13,Fseems to be reluctant to agree that
OL,14,Fthat figure is correct."
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FHe added: "It does strike a strange
OL,7,Fchord when some political leaders from
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland today will be saying
OL,9,Fthat this Prime Minister needs to
OL,10,Fprovide financial support, when he can
OL,11,Fstand back and say, I have done so,
OL,12,Fand #81 million is available for the
OL,13,Fpeople of Northern Ireland, and it's
OL,14,Fup to your leaders to determine how
OL,15,Fbest that support should be dispensed
OL,16,Fat this time of need."
OL,26,@nD@KOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland First Minister and
OL,7,FSinn Fein vice president Michelle
OL,8,FO'Neill said there had been a "bit of
OL,9,Fmessing around" on how Westminster
OL,10,Fsupports are enacted in Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,F"The previous announcement of #81
OL,14,Fmillion, that was #150 credit off
OL,15,Fpeople's electricity bills in England,
OL,16,Fbut over here it translates to #30,"
OL,17,FMs O'Neill said.
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@OO]uD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,F"So we challenged the Prime Minister
OL,7,Ftoday very directly on that point,
OL,8,Fthey need to bring forward a piece of
OL,9,Flegislation that allows us to actually
OL,10,Fget that #30, the previous
OL,11,Fannouncement, out into people's
OL,12,Fpockets."
OL,14,FShe added: "Every family that we spoke
OL,15,Fto, every individual that we're
OL,16,Fspeaking to, are really struggling
OL,17,Fright now, they were already
OL,18,Fstruggling, and now what's
OL,19,Finternationally is having a real life
OL,20,Fimpact on their day to day lives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]vD@LOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FMs McDonald added: "It's not good
OL,7,Fenough, you know, to talk a big game
OL,8,Faround supporting people in this cost
OL,9,Fof living crisis and then short change
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"There's no sense in Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fcoming here a day late and a dollar
OL,14,Fshort."
OL,16,FAlliance Party leader and Justice
OL,17,FMinister Naomi Long said that their
OL,18,Fmeeting with Sir Keir was "short" but
OL,19,F"packed" and he seemed "very open" to
OL,20,Fthe issues raised.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@AOUvD@GO]zD@[OUzD@aO]{D@AOU{D@
OL,26,AHO]{D@XOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
