PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,F"We are the most reliant region of the
OL,7,FUK on home heating oil and it does
OL,8,Fcreate real challenges for us," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"What we need to do is both focus on
OL,12,Fthe transition to better fuel
OL,13,Fopportunities, and they are out there,
OL,14,Fand we need to invest in that, but we
OL,15,Falso need some kind of short-term
OL,16,Fintervention, that will be properly
OL,17,Fguided by the evidence, but will
OL,18,Fensure that local householders are not
OL,19,Fput under further pressure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@_O]sD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
