FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FMrs Long said among the issues
OL,7,Fdiscussed were the budgetary
OL,8,Fconstraints faced by the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Executive, the stability of
OL,10,Fand reform of the powersharing
OL,11,Finstitutions, and the cost of living
OL,12,Fcrisis.
OL,14,FUUP leader Jon Burrows said he had a
OL,15,F"very frank and constructive
OL,16,Fconversation" with Sir Keir, also
OL,17,Fcalling for support with costs of home
OL,18,Fheating oil, as well as for "a greater
OL,19,Fproportion" of defence expenditure to
OL,20,Fbe spent in Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@MO]zD@]OU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
