PN,44814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FHe also said the UK Government needs
OL,7,Fto find "their backbone in dealing
OL,8,Fwith legacy" and should "stand up to
OL,9,Fthe Irish government and ensure that
OL,10,Fthey fully cooperate with trying to
OL,11,Fget truth and justice for victims of
OL,12,Fterrorism".
OL,14,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna joined the
OL,15,FExecutive parties in calling for
OL,16,Fsupport with energy prices, adding
OL,17,Fthat "how that has been handled by the
OL,18,FExecutive illustrates the dysfunction
OL,19,Fwe're trying to fix with our reform
OL,20,Fproposals".
OL,26,@oD@IOUpD@LO]pD@YOUtD@JO]yD@FOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
