CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773360185
OL,3,CStarmer visit 'raises expectations' he
OL,4,Cwill act on high fuel costs - Sinn Fein
OL,6,FMr Robinson said he also discussed the
OL,7,Fpowersharing institutions, the
OL,8,Fbudgetary shortfall in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, and post-Brexit related
OL,10,F"nonsensical hangovers" on trade with
OL,11,FGreat Britain.
OL,13,FMs McDonald said they raised issues
OL,14,Frelating to Palestine, Iran and the
OL,15,FUK's arming of Israel, as well as the
OL,16,Fprogress in establishing the Pat
OL,17,FFinucane inquiry and the need for an
OL,18,Finquiry into the death of Sean Brown,
OL,19,Fa Catholic father murdered by
OL,20,Floyalists in 1997.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@WO]
